---
import { SEGMENTS } from '../data/segments';
---
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="mb-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Kies jouw sector</span>
        <h2 class="h2 mt-2">Eén tool, vier sector-varianten.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-md text-sm text-primary/60">
        De kern-forecast is hetzelfde. Sector-specifieke data (weer-gevoeligheid, rijping, event-types) en de fiscale finesses verschillen per variant.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      {SEGMENTS.map((s) => (
        <a
          href={`/voor/${s.slug}/`}
          class="group flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-white p-6 transition hover:border-accent hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="h-5 w-5"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M8 3v4M16 3v4M3 11h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">{s.shortLabel}</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 flex-1 text-sm text-primary/70">{s.tileDescription}</p>
          <span class="mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-accent group-hover:underline">Bekijk variant &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
